(135, 1, '2013-11-19 19:35:39', '2013-11-19 11:35:39', '<span style="color: #ff0000;">微信营销行业基础解决方案</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>餐饮行业解决方案</strong>\r\n\r\n<span>针对餐饮行业，微西安能够提供定制性的<a href="http://www.star.sn.cn/em/weixin/" target="_blank">微信</a>解决方案，实现微信优惠券、会员卡、微信预约订桌、微信菜品查询、店面地理位置查询、促销折扣信息发布等一系列功能，并确保折扣信息100%到达终端客户手中。</span>\r\n\r\n<span>&lt;ignore_js_op&gt;<img id="aimg_876" alt="" src="http://www.star.sn.cn/data/attachment/forum/201311/13/161518x2g7ac4lr61343q8.jpg" width="270" height="405" /> &lt;ignore_js_op&gt;<img id="aimg_877" alt="" src="http://www.star.sn.cn/data/attachment/forum/201311/13/161519d62g6s3v3uyw8o66.jpg" width="270" height="405" /> </span>\r\n\r\n<span><span><strong>本地生活解决方案</strong></span></span>\r\n<div align="left"><span style="font-family: inherit;">针对本地生活O2O，微西安能够提供定制性的微信解决方案，实现微信优惠券、会员卡、微信预约订桌、微信菜品查询、店面地理位置查询、促销折扣信息发布等一系列功能，并确保折扣信息100%到达终端客户手中。</span></div>\r\n<span><span><span style="font-family: inherit;">&lt;ignore_js_op&gt;<img id="aimg_878" alt="" src="http://www.star.sn.cn/data/attachment/forum/201311/13/161519h3tofyumr7492ozx.jpg" width="227" /> &lt;ignore_js_op&gt;<img id="aimg_879" alt="" src="http://www.star.sn.cn/data/attachment/forum/201311/13/161519d1898rrp54e4pe14.jpg" width="227" /> </span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: inherit;"><strong>汽车4S解决方案</strong></span></span></span>\r\n<div align="left"><span style="font-family: inherit;">针对汽车行业的需求，微西安开发汽车行业微信服务系统，在微信端实现预约试驾、周边4S店查询、周边加油站查询、查油耗、查违章、智能疲劳监测、自动泊车、微信导航、电台音乐、微信赛车游戏等一系列功能，同时还可以在微信端建立微信车友会，实现车友们的在线交流和互动，也提升汽车品牌的凝聚力。</span></div>\r\n<span><span><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;">&lt;ignore_js_op&gt;<img id="aimg_880" alt="" src="http://www.star.sn.cn/data/attachment/forum/201311/13/161519ppmg6s3664w6zu4w.jpg" width="227" /> &lt;ignore_js_op&gt;<img id="aimg_881" alt="" src="http://www.star.sn.cn/data/attachment/forum/201311/13/161519rbbz8artu4kc4umh.jpg" width="227" /> </span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: inherit;"><strong>地产行业解决方案</strong></span></span></span></span>\r\n<div align="left"><span style="font-family: inherit;">微西安针对房地产行业定制开发房产微信管家系统，用户可以在微信端查看各种户型、看房预约、微信端排号，可以实现在微信端查询周边交通设施、查询地区楼盘房价行情、物业管理等功能，能够使房产信息第一时间百分之百到达潜在客户手中，同时也便利需要买房的终端用户。</span></div>\r\n<span><span><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;">&lt;ignore_js_op&gt;<img id="aimg_882" alt="" src="http://www.star.sn.cn/data/attachment/forum/201311/13/161519byr6vygr4nyl87vg.jpg" width="227" /> &lt;ignore_js_op&gt;<img id="aimg_883" alt="" src="http://www.star.sn.cn/data/attachment/forum/201311/13/161519vl50cuvu3zejjx2d.jpg" width="227" /> </span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: inherit;"><strong>教育行业解决方案</strong></span></span></span></span></span>\r\n<div align="left"><span style="font-family: inherit;">针对教育的需求，微西安提供教育行业微信服务解决方案，可以对学校、教育机构提供便捷的移动端教学评估、课程查询、课程预约、成绩查询等功能，同时提供家长、学生、老师之间私密的三方交流通道，增进彼此之间的感情互动。</span></div>\r\n<span><span><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;">&lt;ignore_js_op&gt;<img id="aimg_884" alt="" src="http://www.star.sn.cn/data/attachment/forum/201311/13/161519iawo9mhpmwpbik1k.jpg" width="227" /> &lt;ignore_js_op&gt;<img id="aimg_885" alt="" src="http://www.star.sn.cn/data/attachment/forum/201311/13/161519z18696y91y8uy9qu.jpg" width="227" /> </span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: inherit;"><strong>医药行业解决方案</strong></span></span></span></span></span></span>\r\n<div align="left"><span style="font-family: inherit;">微西安针对医药行业定制开发医药微信服务体系，实现医药品牌推广、疾病库症状库打通接入、产品功效查询、真伪查询、微信线上咨询问诊服务、电话咨询问诊咨询接入、微信名医座谈会、微访谈、微访谈线上挂号、预约看诊等功能。</span></div>\r\n<span><span><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;">&lt;ignore_js_op&gt;<img id="aimg_886" alt="" src="http://www.star.sn.cn/data/attachment/forum/201311/13/161519sdx10zn16q1asfs1.png" width="227" /> &lt;ignore_js_op&gt;<img id="aimg_887" alt="" src="http://www.star.sn.cn/data/attachment/forum/201311/13/161519dj0pqe3rj8kzajzj.png" width="227" /> </span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: inherit;"><strong>家具行业解决方案</strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>\r\n<div align="left"><span style="font-family: inherit;">微西安家居行业微信系统，在微信公众平台上为企业建立家居商城，展示企业的产品，发布促销信息，实现产品展示和产品销售一体化系统打通，客户可一键购买家具；同时，微西安独家开发物流查询系统，在微信端即可便捷查询所购货物的物流状态。另外，可实现微信端家居DIY设计，家居风水查询等功能。</span></div>\r\n<span><span><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;">&lt;ignore_js_op&gt;<img id="aimg_888" alt="" src="http://www.star.sn.cn/data/attachment/forum/201311/13/161520xezpize32omzk8p0.jpg" width="227" /> &lt;ignore_js_op&gt;<img id="aimg_889" alt="" src="http://www.star.sn.cn/data/attachment/forum/201311/13/161520tj43n0t383e3yzxy.jpg" width="227" /> </span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: inherit;"><strong>旅游行业解决方案</strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>\r\n<div align="left"><span style="font-family: inherit;">微西安针对旅游行业，独家开发景区管理系统、导游系统、交友系统，可帮助来景区的游客快捷实现景区旅游导航、语音导游、景区天气查询、景区娱乐场所查询、景区门票一键购买、机票酒店查询预订等一系列功能，提升景区的趣味性、科技性、知名度，增强景区和游客之间的互通有无。</span></div>\r\n<span><span><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;">&lt;ignore_js_op&gt;<img id="aimg_890" alt="" src="http://www.star.sn.cn/data/attachment/forum/201311/13/161520b7wik7wxk37x7n3t.jpg" width="227" /> &lt;ignore_js_op&gt;<img id="aimg_891" alt="" src="http://www.star.sn.cn/data/attachment/forum/201311/13/161520ue2d152w2qpws6yp.jpg" width="227" /> </span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: inherit;"><strong>商超行业解决方案</strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>\r\n<div align="left"><span style="font-family: inherit;">针对商场超市，微西安独家开发商超微信服务体系，在公众平台和3G移动门户网站上实现促销信息发布、产品查询、商场室内导航、周边便民服务查询等功能；同时绑定商超会员卡系统，在微信端对会员进行统一的管理和信息发布。</span></div>\r\n<span><span><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;">&lt;ignore_js_op&gt;<img id="aimg_892" alt="" src="http://www.star.sn.cn/data/attachment/forum/201311/13/161520zpcnbyl88uucbuc1.jpg" width="227" /> &lt;ignore_js_op&gt;<img id="aimg_893" alt="" src="http://www.star.sn.cn/data/attachment/forum/201311/13/161520tcioh6tck4ltstli.jpg" width="227" /> </span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: inherit;"><strong>白酒行业解决方案</strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>\r\n<div align="left"><span style="font-family: inherit;">针对白酒行业，微西安独家开发白酒行业微信服务体系，助力白酒品牌进行有效的品牌推广和电商销售，实现CRM客服系统打通、微信商城搭建、产品查询、销售支付、订单物流查询、真伪验证等功能，同时针对白酒品牌的全国经销商，开发经销商管理体系，对其进行微信端口行之有效的管理。</span></div>\r\n<span><span><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;">&lt;ignore_js_op&gt;<img id="aimg_894" alt="" src="http://www.star.sn.cn/data/attachment/forum/201311/13/161520wf77pvxq37q77w13.jpg" width="227" /> &lt;ignore_js_op&gt;<img id="aimg_895" alt="" src="http://www.star.sn.cn/data/attachment/forum/201311/13/161520p7qbi5b0nmzys59t.jpg" width="227" /> </span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: inherit;"><strong>银行行业解决方案</strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>\r\n<div align="left"><span style="font-family: inherit;">微西安银行系统微信解决方案，实现在微信公众平台上银行业务系统整体打通，为用户提供开卡退卡、账户查询、预约取款、附近网点、汇率汇评等一系列功能，提高电子银行用户的用户体验，也提升银行的品牌美誉度。</span></div>\r\n<span><span><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;">&lt;ignore_js_op&gt;<img id="aimg_896" alt="" src="http://www.star.sn.cn/data/attachment/forum/201311/13/161520kt7zze6e6ab51khj.jpg" width="227" /> &lt;ignore_js_op&gt;<img id="aimg_897" alt="" src="http://www.star.sn.cn/data/attachment/forum/201311/13/161520tlnnr2ciulmpiyu2.jpg" width="227" /> </span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: inherit;"><strong>保健行业解决方案</strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>\r\n<div align="left"><span style="font-family: inherit;">针对保健品行业，微西安独家开发保健品微信服务体系，在微信端搭建3G移动门户网站，实现行业内新闻发布、品牌宣传推广和销售体系一站式打通、产品查询、微信名医座谈会、微访谈等功能。</span></div>\r\n<span><span><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;">&lt;ignore_js_op&gt;<img id="aimg_898" alt="" src="http://www.star.sn.cn/data/attachment/forum/201311/13/161521v3ppt3q208950205.jpg" width="205" /> &lt;ignore_js_op&gt;<img id="aimg_899" alt="" src="http://www.star.sn.cn/data/attachment/forum/201311/13/161521gov9ihviuhx6gcui.jpg" width="227" /> </span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: inherit;"><strong>金融行业解决方案</strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>\r\n<div align="left"><span style="font-family: inherit;">针对金融证券企业需求，，微西安系统提供微信端开户销户、理财产品销售、理财专家产品分析、周边证券网点查询、用户行为分析监测、证券信息分组订阅、股票走势分析、汇率汇评等便民终端服务项目，方便企业和客户之间的互动交流。</span></div>\r\n<span><span><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;">&lt;ignore_js_op&gt;<img id="aimg_900" alt="" src="http://www.star.sn.cn/data/attachment/forum/201311/13/161521wenk2n919mnsmfj9.jpg" width="227" /> &lt;ignore_js_op&gt;<img id="aimg_901" alt="" src="http://www.star.sn.cn/data/attachment/forum/201311/13/161521n2jgi8ffdyii92hj.jpg" width="227" /> </span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: inherit;"><strong>招聘行业解决方案</strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>\r\n<div align="left"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><a href="http://vxa.me/108.htm" target="_blank">微西安</a>针对招聘行业，定制开发了微信HR管家系统，实现微信招聘模块的开发接入，包括宣讲会预定、招聘信息通告、准员工社区管理、企业文化、面试知识 、内部招聘、录用状态查询等等。</span></div>\r\n<span><span><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;">&lt;ignore_js_op&gt;<img id="aimg_902" alt="" src="http://www.star.sn.cn/data/attachment/forum/201311/13/161521sb6yadd2dt6d78tv.jpg" width="227" /> &lt;ignore_js_op&gt;<img id="aimg_903" alt="" src="http://www.star.sn.cn/data/attachment/forum/201311/13/161521nwnkkklawanhnlkk.jpg" width="227" /> </span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: inherit;"><strong>快消行业解决方案</strong></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>\r\n<div align="left"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><a href="http://vxa.me/108.htm" target="_blank">微西安</a>独家开发快消行业微信服务全套解决方案，能满足快消品牌客户实现品牌推广、CRM客服系统打通接入、微信商城打通、产品查询、销售支付、订单物流查询、真伪查询、经销商管理体系管理等各种需求。</span></div>\r\n<span><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span style="font-family: inherit;">&lt;ignore_js_op&gt;<img id="aimg_904" alt="" src="http://www.star.sn.cn/data/attachment/forum/201311/13/161521dlliy009blbbql1v.png" width="227" /> &lt;ignore_js_op&gt;<img id="aimg_905" alt="" src="http://www.star.sn.cn/data/attachment/forum/201311/13/161521tcnbwm1buqef1wqq.png" width="227" /></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>', '微信营销行业基础解决方案', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '108-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-11-19 19:35:39', '2013-11-19 11:35:39', '', 108, 'http://www.vxa.me/135.htm', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
